data.description: This three bedroom, two bath brick rancher is a charmer! New flooring and cabinets plus butcher block countertop in the kitchen, both bathrooms renovated, gleaming hardwood floors and a bonus room/office make this warm and inviting house the perfect place to call HOME. You will love the attention to detail in this move-in ready home!!! Everything you need is so close- restaurants, supermarket, CNU, Riverside Hospital, City Center and access to Interstate. VA and FHA buyers are WELCOME but seller STRONGLY prefers local lenders.
